<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AIで月収が3倍になったフリーランスが続出中 | AIDXschool</title>
    
    <meta name="description" content="30秒で体験できるAI自動化。レポート作成、SNS投稿、請求書作成を自動化して、好きな仕事だけする人生へ。プログラミング不要、今すぐ無料で始められます。">
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <script src="../assets/enhanced-visuals.js" defer></script>
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #6366F1;
            --primary-dark: #4F46E5;
            --primary-light: #818CF8;
            --secondary: #10B981;
            --secondary-light: #34D399;
            --accent: #F59E0B;
            --accent-light: #FCD34D;
            --danger: #EF4444;
            --dark: #0F172A;
            --gray-900: #1E293B;
            --gray-800: #334155;
            --gray-700: #475569;
            --gray-600: #64748B;
            --gray-500: #94A3B8;
            --gray-400: #CBD5E1;
            --gray-300: #E2E8F0;
            --gray-200: #F1F5F9;
            --gray-100: #F8FAFC;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            
            --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%);
            --gradient-secondary: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary) 0%, var(--secondary-light) 100%);
            --gradient-accent: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-light) 100%);
            --gradient-dark: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark) 0%, var(--gray-900) 100%);
            
            --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --shadow-xl: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
            color: var(--dark);
            background: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        /* ヒーローセクション */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: var(--gradient-dark);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="100" height="100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><pattern id="grid" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 100 0 L 0 0 0 100" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)" stroke-width="1"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(%23grid)"/></svg>');
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--white);
        }
        
        .live-counter {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .live-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: var(--secondary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.5); }
        }
        
        .live-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 64px);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--white), var(--gray-300));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 24px);
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--gray-400);
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }
        
        .hero-cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .hero-cta::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.6s, height 0.6s;
        }
        
        .hero-cta:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
        }
        
        .hero-cta:hover::before {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
        }
        
        .hero-cta-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        /* ライブデモセクション */
        .demo-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: var(--gray-100);
        }
        
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--dark);
        }
        
        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }
        
        .demo-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .demo-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .demo-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        
        .demo-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
        }
        
        .demo-card:hover::before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }
        
        .demo-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .demo-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--dark);
        }
        
        .demo-desc {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .demo-time {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--gray-100);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        /* デモプレビューモーダル */
        .demo-preview {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            z-index: 1000;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .demo-preview.active {
            display: flex;
        }
        
        .demo-content {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 24px;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            max-height: 90vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .demo-header {
            padding: 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .demo-close {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: none;
            background: var(--gray-100);
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .demo-close:hover {
            background: var(--gray-200);
        }
        
        .demo-body {
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .demo-animation {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            background: var(--gray-100);
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .demo-result {
            background: var(--gradient-secondary);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        .demo-cta {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .demo-cta:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }
        
        /* リアルタイム成功事例 */
        .social-proof {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: var(--white);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .feed-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .feed-item {
            background: var(--gray-100);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            opacity: 0;
            animation: slideUp 0.5s forwards;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        @keyframes slideUp {
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        
        .feed-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .feed-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .feed-info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .feed-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark);
        }
        
        .feed-time {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--gray-500);
        }
        
        .feed-badge {
            background: var(--gradient-secondary);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .feed-content {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--gray-700);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .feed-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
        }
        
        .feed-stat {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gray-600);
        }
        
        .feed-stat-icon {
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        /* コミュニティセクション */
        .community {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: var(--gradient-dark);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .community .section-title {
            color: var(--white);
        }
        
        .community .section-subtitle {
            color: var(--gray-400);
        }
        
        .community-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 32px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 48px auto;
        }
        
        .community-stat {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--primary-light);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--gray-400);
        }
        
        .community-chat {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .chat-message {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .chat-user {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-light);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        /* 3ヶ月後のあなた */
        .future-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: var(--gray-100);
        }
        
        .timeline {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 2px;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--gray-300);
        }
        
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }
        
        .timeline-content {
            flex: 1;
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin: 0 24px;
        }
        
        .timeline-dot {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--white), 0 0 0 6px var(--gray-300);
        }
        
        .timeline-month {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--dark);
        }
        
        .timeline-desc {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gray-600);
        }
        
        /* 収入シミュレーター */
        .simulator {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 48px auto;
        }
        
        .simulator-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .slider-container {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        
        .slider-label {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gray-600);
        }
        
        .slider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
            background: var(--gray-200);
            border-radius: 4px;
            outline: none;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
        }
        
        .slider::-webkit-slider-thumb {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        
        .simulator-result {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: var(--white);
        }
        
        .result-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .result-amount {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }
        
        /* FOMO セクション */
        .fomo-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .countdown-container {
            background: var(--gradient-accent);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: var(--white);
        }
        
        .countdown-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        .countdown {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        .countdown-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .countdown-number {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .countdown-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .spots-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .spots-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        /* FAQ AIチャット */
        .faq-section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: var(--gray-100);
        }
        
        .chat-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .chat-header {
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .chat-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        .chat-status {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .chat-body {
            height: 400px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        
        .chat-bubble {
            max-width: 80%;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .chat-bubble.user {
            margin-left: auto;
        }
        
        .chat-bubble-content {
            background: var(--gray-100);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .chat-bubble.user .chat-bubble-content {
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            color: var(--white);
        }
        
        .chat-input {
            padding: 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .chat-input-field {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--gray-300);
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .chat-input-field:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .chat-send {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border: none;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .chat-send:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        /* 最終CTA */
        .final-cta {
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background: var(--gradient-dark);
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--white);
        }
        
        .final-title {
            font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        .final-desc {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--gray-400);
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        
        .cta-options {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        
        .cta-option {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            width: 300px;
            text-align: left;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .cta-option:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
        
        .cta-option.recommended {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .cta-option.recommended::before {
            content: 'おすすめ';
            position: absolute;
            top: -12px;
            left: 24px;
            background: var(--gradient-primary);
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .cta-option-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .cta-option-price {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--primary-light);
        }
        
        .cta-option-features {
            list-style: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gray-400);
        }
        
        .cta-option-features li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 24px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .cta-option-features li::before {
            content: '✓';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }
        
        .guarantee {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 16px 32px;
